1
00:02:13,600 --> 00:02:14,280
Husband

2
00:02:44,560 --> 00:02:45,320
Hya!

3
00:02:46,760 --> 00:02:47,240
Hya!

4
00:02:49,320 --> 00:02:49,800
Hya!

5
00:02:51,680 --> 00:02:52,160
Hya!

6
00:02:52,640 --> 00:02:53,120
Hya!

7
00:02:59,960 --> 00:03:00,440
Hya!

8
00:03:02,640 --> 00:03:03,120
Hya!

9
00:03:12,320 --> 00:03:13,720
We have become wanted criminals.

10
00:03:15,520 --> 00:03:16,600
I have failed you all.

11
00:03:17,480 --> 00:03:18,280
The arrow is on the string.

12
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:19,840
It must be released.

13
00:03:20,960 --> 00:03:21,600
Right now,

14
00:03:22,640 --> 00:03:24,520
we must beat Shang Hua and Wang Zhi

15
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:27,320
to the Western Depot's secret intelligence mechanism.

16
00:03:35,880 --> 00:03:37,040
Did you hear what I said?

17
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:40,120
I know.

18
00:03:41,840 --> 00:03:43,760
We can't let the eccentric old man have lit the firecracker in vain.

19
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:53,480
The key.

20
00:03:54,040 --> 00:03:54,720
The key.

21
00:03:55,120 --> 00:03:55,800
The key.

22
00:03:59,040 --> 00:03:59,680
Where is the key?

23
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:00,880
How could the key be missing?

24
00:04:01,200 --> 00:04:02,440
How should I know?

25
00:04:02,760 --> 00:04:04,120
It was on me when we reached the palace gate.

26
00:04:04,120 --> 00:04:04,720
And then?

27
00:04:08,040 --> 00:04:08,840
Japanese ninjas.

28
00:04:12,240 --> 00:04:13,640
Japanese ninjas stole the key.

29
00:04:15,440 --> 00:04:16,280
Shen Youzhi.

30
00:04:33,640 --> 00:04:34,800
It's truly ridiculous.

31
00:04:37,280 --> 00:04:39,320
We exhausted our minds and gave everything,

32
00:04:40,040 --> 00:04:41,320
even sacrificed a brother,

33
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:43,680
only to end up with nothing.

34
00:04:44,280 --> 00:04:45,520
How can it be nothing?

35
00:04:46,240 --> 00:04:47,840
The eccentric old man won't have died in vain.

36
00:04:52,240 --> 00:04:53,440
So what do we do now?

37
00:04:54,320 --> 00:04:55,280
The key is gone too.

38
00:04:56,880 --> 00:04:57,480
Even if we reach

39
00:04:57,480 --> 00:04:58,720
the Western Depot's secret intelligence mechanism,

40
00:04:59,240 --> 00:05:00,440
we are helpless.

41
00:05:13,640 --> 00:05:14,960
We might just lose our lives.

42
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:18,480
Brother Lu, go back to your Shuntian Prefecture.

43
00:05:20,200 --> 00:05:21,480
Beauty, go back to your Western Regions.

44
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:23,480
I'll go back to my Tang Clan.

45
00:05:25,200 --> 00:05:26,160
Let's go our separate ways.

46
00:05:32,440 --> 00:05:32,960
Tang Xi.

47
00:05:33,800 --> 00:05:35,200
I think it's the best plan.

48
00:05:35,840 --> 00:05:36,560
Who's there?

49
00:05:37,560 --> 00:05:39,160
The disputes of the noble families in Shu

50
00:05:39,960 --> 00:05:42,800
Rise like dark clouds to the nine heavens.

51
00:05:44,200 --> 00:05:45,440
Heaven's creation makes me the furnace,

52
00:05:45,800 --> 00:05:47,200
A hundred skills cannot compare to this one.

53
00:05:48,200 --> 00:05:49,560
Elder of the Tang Clan's Mechanism Pavilion,

54
00:05:49,840 --> 00:05:51,440
Tang Tiankun greets the Young Mistress.

55
00:05:52,640 --> 00:05:53,960
Third Elder, at your age,

56
00:05:54,760 --> 00:05:56,080
coming all the way from Shu,

57
00:05:56,280 --> 00:05:57,760
surely it must be for something urgent.

58
00:05:59,160 --> 00:06:00,000
Young Mistress,

59
00:06:00,960 --> 00:06:02,000
what you have done,

60
00:06:02,160 --> 00:06:03,440
everyone in the Tang Clan already knows.

61
00:06:04,440 --> 00:06:05,320
Tonight's heroic deed,

62
00:06:05,320 --> 00:06:06,600
I need not say more about it.

63
00:06:07,040 --> 00:06:08,360
If you were all alone,

64
00:06:08,600 --> 00:06:10,040
we would never interfere.

65
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:11,520
But you are the Young Mistress.

66
00:06:11,680 --> 00:06:12,480
The stance of the sect,

67
00:06:12,480 --> 00:06:13,240
the honor and disgrace of the family...

68
00:06:15,160 --> 00:06:17,320
Do not participate in any more Sifang activities.

69
00:06:18,080 --> 00:06:20,160
Since you have all become wanted criminals,

70
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:22,840
you might as well find a way to lay low.

71
00:06:23,400 --> 00:06:25,120
The Tang Clan can help with this.

72
00:06:25,960 --> 00:06:27,560
But to contend with the Eastern Depot,

73
00:06:28,280 --> 00:06:29,240
I'm afraid that is impossible.

74
00:06:43,040 --> 00:06:44,880
The foundation of the Eastern Depot

75
00:06:48,600 --> 00:06:52,240
is to serve the country and the people.

76
00:06:55,040 --> 00:06:56,440
As a Depot guard,

77
00:06:57,720 --> 00:06:59,320
one must be loyal, righteous, brave, and wise.

78
00:06:59,640 --> 00:07:00,400
Pure,

79
00:07:01,440 --> 00:07:02,600
upright and unbending.

80
00:07:04,040 --> 00:07:05,240
In conduct,

81
00:07:06,440 --> 00:07:07,480
never wrong the innocent,

82
00:07:09,360 --> 00:07:10,400
never let the guilty go.

83
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:14,280
Only in this way

84
00:07:16,280 --> 00:07:18,240
can one be like Yue Fei,

85
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:27,400
leaving a good name for a hundred generations.

86
00:08:29,160 --> 00:08:29,680
Young Mistress,

87
00:08:30,520 --> 00:08:31,400
going back this time

88
00:08:31,760 --> 00:08:32,760
is extremely dangerous.

89
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:35,240
Do you still want to hide yourself in the city?

90
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:38,560
If you insist on going with them,

91
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:41,440
then don't blame me for being impolite.

92
00:08:41,880 --> 00:08:43,160
Actually, the three elders

93
00:08:43,240 --> 00:08:45,400
have been waiting in the dark for your answer.

94
00:09:13,040 --> 00:09:13,640
Is it sweet?

95
00:09:16,280 --> 00:09:17,040
It is sweet.

96
00:09:19,920 --> 00:09:20,720
It's salty.

97
00:09:26,040 --> 00:09:26,760
I lied to you.

98
00:09:28,160 --> 00:09:29,480
This is just ordinary candy.

99
00:09:31,720 --> 00:09:33,640
You eat it every day, how can you not tell?

100
00:09:37,640 --> 00:09:39,280
Because you have no sense of taste at all.

101
00:09:40,040 --> 00:09:41,440
A person who eats without flavor,

102
00:09:42,160 --> 00:09:43,880
pretending to relish every bite every day.

103
00:09:48,760 --> 00:09:50,040
Using your bravado

104
00:09:51,520 --> 00:09:53,000
to hold onto your last breath.

105
00:09:59,760 --> 00:10:00,840
We've all gone mad.

106
00:10:05,880 --> 00:10:06,760
Let's go.

107
00:10:09,360 --> 00:10:10,360
I want to go back to the Shu Mountains.

108
00:10:12,440 --> 00:10:13,560
I want to eat dandan noodles.

109
00:10:15,920 --> 00:10:17,280
I want to see the tapirs on the back mountain.

110
00:10:17,280 --> 00:10:18,280
To see if they've gotten any fatter.

111
00:10:26,920 --> 00:10:27,560
Beauty,

112
00:10:27,960 --> 00:10:28,760
will you come with me,

113
00:10:28,800 --> 00:10:29,640
or go back to the Western Regions?

114
00:10:30,960 --> 00:10:32,000
I'm definitely going with you.

115
00:10:32,280 --> 00:10:33,600
I promised my brother-in-law I'd look after you.

116
00:10:34,880 --> 00:10:35,400
Young Mistress.

117
00:10:36,600 --> 00:10:37,120
Young Mistress.

118
00:10:39,560 --> 00:10:40,160
You cannot leave.

119
00:10:41,080 --> 00:10:42,120
You have the highest martial arts skills here.

120
00:10:42,560 --> 00:10:43,160
If you leave,

121
00:10:44,800 --> 00:10:45,440
what will we do?

122
00:10:47,240 --> 00:10:48,080
The game is over.

123
00:10:49,360 --> 00:10:50,080
It's time to go home.

124
00:10:51,680 --> 00:10:52,920
You have a wife and children too.

125
00:10:53,560 --> 00:10:54,360
Fend for yourself.

126
00:10:54,440 --> 00:10:55,680
What do you mean "fend for yourself"?

127
00:10:57,200 --> 00:10:57,880
Didn't you say

128
00:10:58,560 --> 00:10:59,840
we were like-minded people?

129
00:11:02,480 --> 00:11:04,120
Let's all calm down a bit.

130
00:11:05,480 --> 00:11:06,440
As long as we are together,

131
00:11:07,120 --> 00:11:07,640
there will always be a way.

132
00:11:07,640 --> 00:11:08,280
Let her go.

133
00:11:08,360 --> 00:11:09,240
Don't talk nonsense.

134
00:11:09,240 --> 00:11:10,040
Can you make her stay?

135
00:11:10,600 --> 00:11:11,880
Can you take responsibility for her clan?

136
00:11:52,080 --> 00:11:52,640
Godfather.

137
00:11:53,640 --> 00:11:55,920
Even Consort Wan dares not protect him now.

138
00:11:56,520 --> 00:11:58,000
Keeping him here at this time,

139
00:11:58,720 --> 00:12:00,440
I fear will cause endless trouble.

140
00:12:03,600 --> 00:12:04,840
Do you think I don't know that?

141
00:12:05,640 --> 00:12:08,240
They planted an inner demon in Consort Wan.

142
00:12:10,120 --> 00:12:11,480
Despite all my calculations,

143
00:12:12,320 --> 00:12:14,720
I didn't expect Wu Qiangu to use Zhuyou Shu.

144
00:12:14,920 --> 00:12:17,160
Allowing Tang Xi and the others

145
00:12:17,360 --> 00:12:18,560
to remove the sore from Consort Wan's heart

146
00:12:18,880 --> 00:12:20,160
and plant a demon instead.

147
00:12:23,880 --> 00:12:27,280
I underestimated his skills back then.

148
00:12:28,160 --> 00:12:31,040
I thought they were just tricks and sleight of hand,

149
00:12:31,400 --> 00:12:33,800
I didn't expect them to be so profound.

150
00:12:35,600 --> 00:12:38,400
It's a pity he died.

151
00:12:40,720 --> 00:12:44,280
The Western Depot will certainly be abolished.

152
00:12:45,960 --> 00:12:47,360
The reason you are here today

153
00:12:47,840 --> 00:12:48,800
is for me to tell you

154
00:12:49,400 --> 00:12:50,880
to bring back what belongs to me.

155
00:12:52,600 --> 00:12:54,080
I do still have some

156
00:12:54,080 --> 00:12:55,720
reliable forces I can hand over to you.

157
00:12:56,000 --> 00:12:58,920
But how do you intend to settle me?

158
00:12:59,760 --> 00:13:00,880
Settle you?

159
00:13:03,240 --> 00:13:05,960
I'm afraid you've already settled yourself

160
00:13:06,240 --> 00:13:07,400
to go to the Eastern Ocean, haven't you?

161
00:13:08,280 --> 00:13:09,800
If it weren't for the long journey

162
00:13:10,200 --> 00:13:11,720
requiring more manpower

163
00:13:12,120 --> 00:13:15,560
to transport your gold, silver, and jewels,

164
00:13:19,440 --> 00:13:21,520
You detained me at the Eastern Depot,

165
00:13:21,520 --> 00:13:22,520
what was it for?

166
00:13:23,320 --> 00:13:25,720
To pay me back for the grievances I caused you all these years?

167
00:13:26,240 --> 00:13:28,240
Or to use me to teach your godson a lesson?

168
00:13:28,600 --> 00:13:29,800
To let him understand

169
00:13:30,480 --> 00:13:31,800
that being your enemy

170
00:13:32,400 --> 00:13:34,200
ends up like this?

171
00:13:38,760 --> 00:13:40,360
To take back what I want.

172
00:13:40,920 --> 00:13:42,040
And to eliminate future trouble.

173
00:13:47,360 --> 00:13:49,600
Zhang Yi, Tang Xi, and the others have escaped.

174
00:13:50,040 --> 00:13:51,720
But the key was left behind.

175
00:13:52,880 --> 00:13:53,760
This matter

176
00:13:54,560 --> 00:13:56,080
is extremely suspicious.

177
00:13:56,600 --> 00:13:58,120
What matters is the result,

178
00:14:00,160 --> 00:14:01,160
not the process.

179
00:14:01,840 --> 00:14:03,040
Some changes

180
00:14:03,640 --> 00:14:05,640
often happen during the process.

181
00:14:06,200 --> 00:14:08,280
My Eastern Depot will not let them stay out there,

182
00:14:08,280 --> 00:14:09,400
living free and happy.

183
00:14:10,560 --> 00:14:11,520
Pass down the order.

184
00:14:12,000 --> 00:14:13,000
A reward of a thousand taels of silver

185
00:14:13,200 --> 00:14:16,040
for the capture of Tang Xi, Yuan Ran, and Zhang Yi.

186
00:14:16,360 --> 00:14:17,280
Whoever brings their heads

187
00:14:18,520 --> 00:14:19,400
will be made a Battalion Commander.

188
00:14:21,880 --> 00:14:22,320
Zhang Yi!

189
00:14:22,880 --> 00:14:23,320
Zhang Yi!

190
00:14:23,960 --> 00:14:24,400
Zhang Yi!

191
00:14:24,560 --> 00:14:25,440
Where are you going, Zhang Yi?

192
00:14:26,360 --> 00:14:27,960
The Eastern Depot is surely hunting you, Zhang Yi.

193
00:14:28,120 --> 00:14:29,280
Zhang Yi, don't go yet, Zhang Yi!

194
00:14:29,960 --> 00:14:31,120
Why not hide out at my place for a while?

195
00:14:31,320 --> 00:14:32,240
We can plan our next move.

196
00:14:32,760 --> 00:14:33,160
I know.

197
00:14:33,440 --> 00:14:34,520
You might be unhappy right now.

198
00:14:34,720 --> 00:14:35,400
Our current result

199
00:14:35,400 --> 00:14:36,720
might be even worse than three years ago.

200
00:14:37,440 --> 00:14:38,120
But it doesn't matter.

201
00:14:38,560 --> 00:14:39,040
Us two brothers

202
00:14:39,080 --> 00:14:40,040
can find a quiet place

203
00:14:40,200 --> 00:14:41,200
and plan our next move first.

204
00:14:41,400 --> 00:14:42,600
Stop saying "us," "us."

205
00:14:44,280 --> 00:14:45,760
The one with no place to settle down now

206
00:14:45,760 --> 00:14:46,400
is only me.

207
00:14:47,120 --> 00:14:47,640
Not you.

208
00:14:50,080 --> 00:14:50,560
No...

209
00:14:51,200 --> 00:14:52,760
what are you saying?

210
00:14:52,800 --> 00:14:53,600
The honest truth.

211
00:14:56,680 --> 00:14:57,440
Three years ago,

212
00:14:58,720 --> 00:14:59,400
you were the one who proposed the plan.

213
00:15:00,640 --> 00:15:02,320
You were also the one standing by Wang Zhi's side.

214
00:15:03,000 --> 00:15:04,640
And tonight, the one standing outside the palace was still you.

215
00:15:06,360 --> 00:15:07,960
You always keep yourself out of it.

216
00:15:08,920 --> 00:15:09,240
No...

217
00:15:09,520 --> 00:15:10,480
I wanted to go in too!

218
00:15:10,680 --> 00:15:11,840
But you guys said I don't know martial arts,

219
00:15:11,840 --> 00:15:12,720
and told me to stay outside!

220
00:15:12,720 --> 00:15:14,200
You always use your weakness as an excuse

221
00:15:14,520 --> 00:15:15,560
to make us look out for you and care for you.

222
00:15:15,960 --> 00:15:16,600
If that's the case,

223
00:15:16,600 --> 00:15:17,880
why did you choose to get involved?

224
00:15:18,480 --> 00:15:20,000
Your participation is meaningless to us.

225
00:15:20,920 --> 00:15:21,960
It's even a burden.

226
00:15:24,000 --> 00:15:24,640
I know...

227
00:15:25,280 --> 00:15:26,680
you're definitely unhappy tonight.

228
00:15:27,520 --> 00:15:28,280
If you want to vent,

229
00:15:29,520 --> 00:15:30,440
just let it all out.

230
00:15:30,680 --> 00:15:31,120
It's okay.

231
00:15:31,200 --> 00:15:31,640
I ask you,

232
00:15:33,000 --> 00:15:33,920
what can you do?

233
00:15:34,640 --> 00:15:35,720
If the pursuers catch up now,

234
00:15:36,200 --> 00:15:37,720
should I choose to run for my life,

235
00:15:38,000 --> 00:15:38,960
or choose to die alongside you,

236
00:15:38,960 --> 00:15:40,320
who knows no martial arts?

237
00:15:43,280 --> 00:15:44,520
Since you can't help me with anything,

238
00:15:44,560 --> 00:15:45,520
why are you following me?

239
00:15:46,200 --> 00:15:46,880
No, Zhang Yi, listen...

240
00:15:46,880 --> 00:15:47,680
Hurry up and go.

241
00:15:52,680 --> 00:15:53,240
Get lost!

242
00:16:00,520 --> 00:16:01,160
Zhang Yi...

243
00:16:02,120 --> 00:16:03,240
This is all the money I have on me.

244
00:16:04,880 --> 00:16:05,760
Take it all.

245
00:16:08,080 --> 00:16:08,840
Be careful.

246
00:16:11,040 --> 00:16:11,800
Take care!

247
00:16:29,320 --> 00:16:30,000
You're here.

248
00:16:31,040 --> 00:16:32,120
It's already dawn.

249
00:16:33,160 --> 00:16:33,760
Let me ask you.

250
00:16:34,760 --> 00:16:36,200
The ninjas who attacked Huamanlou that day,

251
00:16:36,280 --> 00:16:37,560
they weren't trying to test me,

252
00:16:38,000 --> 00:16:39,640
but wanted to silence us all.

253
00:16:40,200 --> 00:16:41,400
Just like in the palace last night.

254
00:16:41,400 --> 00:16:41,880
Right?

255
00:16:43,040 --> 00:16:43,720
That's right.

256
00:16:44,520 --> 00:16:45,600
Right now, I...

257
00:16:46,200 --> 00:16:47,560
should be working for Shang Hua.

258
00:16:48,960 --> 00:16:50,400
Actually, from the very beginning,

259
00:16:50,840 --> 00:16:52,680
what mattered wasn't the key,

260
00:16:53,920 --> 00:16:55,240
but Wang Zhi himself.

261
00:16:55,800 --> 00:16:58,000
I also have a copy of that key.

262
00:16:58,880 --> 00:17:00,400
But without Wang Zhi to lead the way,

263
00:17:01,080 --> 00:17:02,360
one still cannot reach

264
00:17:02,920 --> 00:17:04,720
the Western Depot's secret intelligence mechanism.

265
00:17:05,560 --> 00:17:06,400
The intelligence...

266
00:17:08,080 --> 00:17:09,320
was wrong from the start.

267
00:17:19,240 --> 00:17:21,560
What a servant of two masters you are, Lady Hua.

268
00:17:22,600 --> 00:17:23,360
Why did you do this?

269
00:17:24,120 --> 00:17:24,880
Our Four Directions operation

270
00:17:24,880 --> 00:17:26,080
was clearly about to succeed.

271
00:17:28,480 --> 00:17:29,320
Succeed?

272
00:17:30,160 --> 00:17:32,120
Did you really think you could succeed?

273
00:17:32,840 --> 00:17:34,040
To bring down the Western Depot,

274
00:17:34,760 --> 00:17:37,200
and make the Eastern Depot and the Guard's court factions

275
00:17:37,640 --> 00:17:38,520
disappear completely?

276
00:17:39,560 --> 00:17:41,720
I knew the moment Shang Hua found me

277
00:17:42,120 --> 00:17:43,680
that we were nothing but his pawns.

278
00:17:45,240 --> 00:17:45,960
Humble,

279
00:17:46,920 --> 00:17:47,680
insignificant.

280
00:17:48,440 --> 00:17:51,720
Why did you join us in the first place?

281
00:17:53,000 --> 00:17:54,800
Maybe I was too desperate back then.

282
00:17:55,640 --> 00:17:56,880
You gave me hope.

283
00:17:58,200 --> 00:17:59,360
But now,

284
00:18:00,040 --> 00:18:01,680
I just want to end all this so badly.

285
00:18:11,360 --> 00:18:12,800
What condition did Shang Hua offer you?

286
00:18:14,240 --> 00:18:16,720
To personally deliver Wang Zhi's head,

287
00:18:16,880 --> 00:18:18,040
with my own hands.

288
00:18:19,120 --> 00:18:20,200
The deadline is

289
00:18:21,440 --> 00:18:22,160
today.

290
00:18:22,880 --> 00:18:23,640
In that case,

291
00:18:24,360 --> 00:18:25,160
then tell me,

292
00:18:25,840 --> 00:18:27,960
where exactly is the Western Depot's secret intelligence mechanism?

293
00:18:28,400 --> 00:18:30,080
Shang Hua has already obtained the key and Wang Zhi.

294
00:18:30,520 --> 00:18:31,960
Today is my last chance.

295
00:18:33,720 --> 00:18:34,640
Zhang Yi,

296
00:18:36,040 --> 00:18:36,920
Wu Qiangu and I

297
00:18:36,920 --> 00:18:38,600
have long been prepared to die.

298
00:18:40,080 --> 00:18:41,560
Those prayer lanterns...

299
00:18:42,520 --> 00:18:43,840
are the soul-sending lanterns Wu Qiangu

300
00:18:43,840 --> 00:18:45,200
wove for herself.

301
00:18:46,840 --> 00:18:47,480
All so that

302
00:18:47,480 --> 00:18:49,880
you might still have a chance to live in this world.

303
00:18:52,160 --> 00:18:52,760
These lanterns...

304
00:18:52,960 --> 00:18:54,720
why do they look different from usual?

305
00:18:55,520 --> 00:18:57,800
Since they are sky lanterns for Consort Wan,

306
00:18:58,560 --> 00:19:00,320
surely special materials must be used.

307
00:19:02,400 --> 00:19:03,480
Remember what I instructed:

308
00:19:06,160 --> 00:19:07,240
When the palace lanterns fly,

309
00:19:08,400 --> 00:19:09,280
all is going well.

310
00:19:11,320 --> 00:19:12,320
Abandon the plan.

311
00:19:12,960 --> 00:19:14,640
I can help you escape the capital

312
00:19:14,840 --> 00:19:15,680
and go to the Western Regions.

313
00:19:16,520 --> 00:19:18,560
Every one of you can live in the moment,

314
00:19:19,120 --> 00:19:20,800
without carrying such heavy burdens.

315
00:19:22,040 --> 00:19:23,480
It is enough for me to go alone.

316
00:19:25,480 --> 00:19:28,120
Lu Shijie can continue his domestic trivia,

317
00:19:28,680 --> 00:19:30,240
his harmonious and happy little days.

318
00:19:31,640 --> 00:19:32,880
Far from strife,

319
00:19:33,280 --> 00:19:34,560
ignoring worldly affairs,

320
00:19:35,080 --> 00:19:37,120
living a stable and prosperous life.

321
00:19:38,880 --> 00:19:39,520
Tang Xi

322
00:19:40,320 --> 00:19:42,400
can continue being her carefree Clan Leader.

323
00:19:43,480 --> 00:19:44,520
With her talent,

324
00:19:45,280 --> 00:19:46,680
she will surely become a grandmaster.

325
00:19:47,160 --> 00:19:48,360
A legend of the martial world.

326
00:19:49,440 --> 00:19:50,280
Yuan Ran

327
00:19:50,520 --> 00:19:52,640
can continue studying her stage puppets,

328
00:19:53,640 --> 00:19:54,800
String Puppetry,

329
00:19:55,640 --> 00:19:57,040
and the characters in her plays.

330
00:19:58,160 --> 00:19:59,400
You can go to the Western Regions.

331
00:19:59,840 --> 00:20:00,960
Though you cannot be an official,

332
00:20:01,080 --> 00:20:02,120
you can still be a chivalrous hero,

333
00:20:02,640 --> 00:20:04,320
protecting the peace of the people.

334
00:20:05,480 --> 00:20:06,800
It's better than being in this capital,

335
00:20:07,000 --> 00:20:08,720
a place that eats people alive.

336
00:20:10,360 --> 00:20:11,200
Now,

337
00:20:13,280 --> 00:20:14,520
the decision is yours.

338
00:20:30,240 --> 00:20:31,960
I heard there were fireworks in the palace last night

339
00:20:32,120 --> 00:20:32,960
Did you see it?

340
00:20:33,400 --> 00:20:34,800
It wasn't fireworks at all

341
00:20:35,080 --> 00:20:36,720
It was assassins breaking into the palace

342
00:20:36,880 --> 00:20:38,480
They startled Consort Wan

343
00:20:38,640 --> 00:20:39,560
The rumor is

344
00:20:39,720 --> 00:20:41,280
that the Western Depot was abolished

345
00:20:41,480 --> 00:20:43,200
and Director-in-chief Wang held a grudge

346
00:20:43,520 --> 00:20:44,840
so he took revenge on Consort Wan

347
00:20:45,600 --> 00:20:46,680
Heaven's justice is clear

348
00:20:46,800 --> 00:20:47,760
Such wild ambition

349
00:20:48,360 --> 00:20:49,080
Finally

350
00:20:49,480 --> 00:20:50,560
he got his retribution

351
00:20:51,360 --> 00:20:51,680
Let's go

352
00:20:51,960 --> 00:20:52,600
Go back inside and sleep

353
00:20:53,160 --> 00:20:53,600
Let's go

354
00:22:05,440 --> 00:22:06,400
Who would have thought

355
00:22:07,200 --> 00:22:09,400
the Western Depot would build their secret mechanism

356
00:22:10,520 --> 00:22:11,960
beneath the Imperial Tombs

357
00:22:13,280 --> 00:22:14,360
In this way

358
00:22:14,760 --> 00:22:16,200
Consort Wan intended to make

359
00:22:16,200 --> 00:22:18,200
the Western Depot her confidant force

360
00:22:19,320 --> 00:22:20,320
What a pity

361
00:22:20,840 --> 00:22:22,760
Consort Wan was suspicious of you

362
00:22:22,920 --> 00:22:23,640
Otherwise

363
00:22:26,240 --> 00:22:27,200
in the future

364
00:22:27,840 --> 00:22:29,560
I fear no one could have shaken you

365
00:22:33,160 --> 00:22:34,640
My good Godfather

366
00:22:35,240 --> 00:22:37,000
Didn't you teach me

367
00:22:37,720 --> 00:22:41,000
that the human heart is the hardest thing to fathom

368
00:22:41,360 --> 00:22:43,160
How could I truly place my hope

369
00:22:43,160 --> 00:22:44,280
on the word "trust"?

370
00:22:45,640 --> 00:22:46,680
Then, in a moment

371
00:22:47,720 --> 00:22:50,280
I will give you an unexpected surprise

372
00:23:27,240 --> 00:23:28,080
Human hearts are different

373
00:23:28,080 --> 00:23:28,920
just like their faces

374
00:23:28,960 --> 00:23:29,840
The Eight Methods of Observing People:

375
00:23:30,080 --> 00:23:32,600
Majesty, Depth, Clarity, Age, Solitude, Meanness, Evil, Vulgarity

376
00:23:33,200 --> 00:23:35,000
At the beginning, human nature is good

377
00:23:35,440 --> 00:23:37,360
We were born with the same face

378
00:23:37,680 --> 00:23:39,200
We can't claim to be radiantly beautiful

379
00:23:39,520 --> 00:23:40,920
but at least innocent and pure

380
00:23:41,840 --> 00:23:43,920
But after a journey through this sea of bureaucracy

381
00:23:44,160 --> 00:23:44,880
it will give birth to

382
00:23:44,880 --> 00:23:46,440
countless faces that are strange to us

383
00:23:47,320 --> 00:23:48,280
Looking at these

384
00:23:49,080 --> 00:23:50,160
don't they look like yourself?

385
00:23:51,600 --> 00:23:52,120
Godfather

386
00:23:53,200 --> 00:23:54,480
Whose spirit tablets are these?

387
00:23:56,640 --> 00:23:58,040
My good Godfather

388
00:23:59,760 --> 00:24:01,560
Look at the names on them

389
00:24:03,880 --> 00:24:06,240
Do you have no memory of them at all?

390
00:24:12,560 --> 00:24:14,360
What is there to be surprised about?

391
00:24:15,320 --> 00:24:17,320
These were all cultivated by my Eastern Depot

392
00:24:17,320 --> 00:24:19,160
death warriors and depot guards

393
00:24:20,000 --> 00:24:21,440
The world does not suffer from a lack of talent

394
00:24:21,560 --> 00:24:22,920
but from a lack of ways to use it

395
00:24:23,880 --> 00:24:26,520
When you possess the means to cultivate talent

396
00:24:27,680 --> 00:24:28,920
why care about

397
00:24:29,040 --> 00:24:30,720
these people who are already dead?

398
00:24:32,640 --> 00:24:34,840
That would only make you

399
00:24:34,840 --> 00:24:37,880
a wailing corpse curled up there. A weakling.

400
00:24:43,800 --> 00:24:45,000
This is Director-in-chief Shang

401
00:24:45,000 --> 00:24:46,760
and what he sees in his eyes

402
00:24:49,560 --> 00:24:50,520
By power

403
00:24:51,480 --> 00:24:52,200
and ability

404
00:24:53,240 --> 00:24:54,720
everything is measured

405
00:24:56,000 --> 00:24:57,720
Look at his appearance now

406
00:24:58,400 --> 00:25:00,520
Healthy body, glowing face

407
00:25:01,200 --> 00:25:02,680
yet his whole being carries

408
00:25:02,680 --> 00:25:05,400
a grim aura that keeps people a thousand miles away

409
00:25:06,360 --> 00:25:07,440
What is it

410
00:25:07,720 --> 00:25:09,680
that made him so twisted

411
00:25:11,120 --> 00:25:12,960
that even the normality of an ordinary person

412
00:25:13,160 --> 00:25:14,560
he is unable to maintain

413
00:25:14,920 --> 00:25:16,360
Wanting to become me

414
00:25:17,640 --> 00:25:19,720
with your intellect and experience

415
00:25:20,200 --> 00:25:21,200
you are still far from it

416
00:25:22,040 --> 00:25:22,880
Cut the crap

417
00:25:25,040 --> 00:25:27,280
Hurry up and take me to get the thing

418
00:25:50,120 --> 00:25:51,760
A sword points to the sky with a laugh

419
00:25:53,760 --> 00:25:55,440
Heaven pities the talent of a hero

420
00:25:57,040 --> 00:25:58,600
Joy emerges from within sorrow

421
00:26:00,160 --> 00:26:01,680
The soul nearly breaks in a dream

422
00:26:10,160 --> 00:26:12,160
Ten years versed in the ways of the world

423
00:26:13,840 --> 00:26:15,240
New leaves cover the old vines

424
00:26:18,040 --> 00:26:19,800
Cultivating the heart, yet not heartless

425
00:26:20,680 --> 00:26:22,240
Dreams return, chasing the flowing water

426
00:26:26,880 --> 00:26:28,360
An April ballad of clouds and snow

427
00:26:30,120 --> 00:26:31,400
Young and reckless

428
00:26:32,440 --> 00:26:34,240
Harboring virtue and ambition, entrusted to the future

429
00:26:35,600 --> 00:26:37,720
Fortune fades in these final times

430
00:26:38,360 --> 00:26:40,360
Glory shines upon us, arriving late

431
00:26:40,680 --> 00:26:42,680
Deep waters, dragon spirit, drifting like duckweed

432
00:26:43,200 --> 00:26:44,720
Flying clouds, emptiness is but empty

433
00:26:45,040 --> 00:26:46,560
Separation and gathering, fate unites

434
00:26:47,120 --> 00:26:48,480
Birds fly to their own woods

435
00:26:48,880 --> 00:26:50,320
Romantic because of deep love

436
00:26:51,720 --> 00:26:53,120
Chang'e regrets fleeing to the moon

437
00:26:54,120 --> 00:26:55,560
Jingwei fills the vast ocean

438
00:26:56,600 --> 00:26:58,000
The blue sea knows no calm

439
00:26:59,200 --> 00:27:01,000
The blue sky offers few paths

440
00:27:20,600 --> 00:27:21,360
Master Zhang

441
00:27:21,640 --> 00:27:22,960
I will see you off here

442
00:27:30,640 --> 00:27:31,480
Many thanks, Flower Lady

443
00:27:49,400 --> 00:27:50,080
Young Mistress

444
00:27:50,360 --> 00:27:51,360
This is a heavenly secret

445
00:27:51,400 --> 00:27:52,360
You cannot burn it

446
00:28:05,040 --> 00:28:06,160
My name is Tang Xi

447
00:28:08,280 --> 00:28:10,600
Because auspicious snow fell when I was born

448
00:28:13,160 --> 00:28:14,240
I laughed and did not cry

449
00:28:18,280 --> 00:28:20,520
The Tang Clan main branch had a daughter after a century

450
00:28:22,200 --> 00:28:23,720
Father was overjoyed

451
00:28:25,640 --> 00:28:27,160
And named me Tang Xi

452
00:28:29,840 --> 00:28:31,640
The Young Mistress is naturally gifted

453
00:28:32,000 --> 00:28:33,080
A martial arts prodigy

454
00:28:33,640 --> 00:28:34,880
With surpassing courage and insight

455
00:28:35,320 --> 00:28:38,000
She has held power in the Tang Clan for three years

456
00:28:38,080 --> 00:28:39,760
Everyone in the Tang Clan obeys her

457
00:28:40,440 --> 00:28:42,360
When we learned Master Konghui passed away

458
00:28:42,600 --> 00:28:43,760
We immediately cast a divination

459
00:28:44,440 --> 00:28:46,400
And knew the Clan Leader faced a mortal tribulation

460
00:28:47,480 --> 00:28:49,080
Even if it defies the heavens

461
00:28:49,560 --> 00:28:51,600
I must bring the Clan Leader back to the Tang Clan

462
00:29:19,480 --> 00:29:20,400
Zhang Yi

463
00:29:21,800 --> 00:29:22,760
For something like this

464
00:29:23,280 --> 00:29:25,000
Shouldn't you wait for everyone to gather?

465
00:29:25,320 --> 00:29:26,320
Wouldn't that be happier?

466
00:29:29,000 --> 00:29:31,160
Did you come alone to die?

467
00:29:31,800 --> 00:29:33,400
Who said he's alone?

468
00:29:34,600 --> 00:29:35,640
Isn't there one more right here?

469
00:29:37,640 --> 00:29:38,520
Wine emboldens the timid

470
00:29:39,160 --> 00:29:40,480
Your sister-in-law insisted I give this to you

471
00:29:41,520 --> 00:29:42,280
She said

472
00:29:42,760 --> 00:29:44,600
I should settle the matters from three years ago

473
00:29:45,120 --> 00:29:45,920
Once and for all

474
00:29:46,680 --> 00:29:47,640
Take this with you too

475
00:29:48,200 --> 00:29:49,680
This is the wine I brewed three years ago

476
00:29:53,000 --> 00:29:53,720
My wife

477
00:29:55,520 --> 00:29:56,280
All these years

478
00:29:57,760 --> 00:29:59,400
I truly believed Zhang Yi would be considerate of me

479
00:30:00,680 --> 00:30:01,800
That he would be invincible

480
00:30:02,320 --> 00:30:03,200
Advancing step by step

481
00:30:03,520 --> 00:30:04,440
Turning defeat into victory

482
00:30:05,800 --> 00:30:06,560
But I was wrong

483
00:30:08,560 --> 00:30:09,880
He too has enemies he cannot defeat

484
00:30:11,680 --> 00:30:12,520
He can fail

485
00:30:13,240 --> 00:30:13,880
He can be reckless

486
00:30:14,840 --> 00:30:16,760
And he can wail like a child

487
00:30:18,600 --> 00:30:19,600
So for him

488
00:30:20,920 --> 00:30:22,160
As his big brother

489
00:30:24,040 --> 00:30:25,080
Shouldn't I be by his side?

490
00:30:30,520 --> 00:30:31,880
I am just as selfish

491
00:30:33,200 --> 00:30:33,960
With Zhang Yi

492
00:30:34,800 --> 00:30:36,320
And the three hundred men of the Divine Machine Battalion

493
00:30:36,880 --> 00:30:38,040
I borrowed you for three years

494
00:30:39,240 --> 00:30:40,560
I am already very satisfied

495
00:30:43,120 --> 00:30:43,760
Daddy

496
00:30:44,080 --> 00:30:45,040
Where are you going?

497
00:30:47,000 --> 00:30:47,600
Tianguan

498
00:30:48,520 --> 00:30:49,560
Remember what Daddy told you

499
00:30:51,040 --> 00:30:51,760
A real man

500
00:30:52,520 --> 00:30:54,080
In the face of a deadly enemy

501
00:30:54,360 --> 00:30:55,200
Can be afraid

502
00:30:55,840 --> 00:30:57,120
But must absolutely never kneel

503
00:30:58,280 --> 00:30:59,400
And certainly cannot run away

504
00:31:01,040 --> 00:31:02,480
Especially when your best friend

505
00:31:02,760 --> 00:31:04,280
Is in danger

506
00:31:04,560 --> 00:31:06,000
You must also try your best to live

507
00:31:08,080 --> 00:31:10,680
Auntie Tang Xi and Godfather Zhang Yi told me that

508
00:31:11,960 --> 00:31:12,760
So

509
00:31:13,720 --> 00:31:14,960
Your Daddy is going to save them

510
00:31:41,360 --> 00:31:41,800
Good wine

511
00:31:42,440 --> 00:31:44,080
It'll hurt less when I get beaten later

512
00:31:48,320 --> 00:31:48,920
Refreshing

513
00:31:50,040 --> 00:31:52,800
I leave the rest to you

514
00:31:54,160 --> 00:31:55,240
Youzhi, bring up the rear

515
00:31:55,560 --> 00:31:56,520
Make it quick

516
00:32:13,040 --> 00:32:14,000
Master Zhang

517
00:32:14,400 --> 00:32:15,720
Since you have already escaped,

518
00:32:17,120 --> 00:32:18,760
why come back to throw your life away?

519
00:32:19,440 --> 00:32:20,960
If I were to give up today,

520
00:32:21,600 --> 00:32:23,840
I would surely die with everlasting regret.

521
00:32:25,720 --> 00:32:26,960
I'd rather risk my life,

522
00:32:27,200 --> 00:32:27,960
and settle this once and for all.

523
00:32:28,720 --> 00:32:29,280
And you?

524
00:32:30,080 --> 00:32:32,040
Why do you fight against me?

525
00:32:32,800 --> 00:32:34,280
Is it for your imperial nobility?

526
00:32:34,800 --> 00:32:35,840
Or for your Godfather?

527
00:32:35,960 --> 00:32:37,440
No matter who I do it for,

528
00:32:38,920 --> 00:32:40,640
you are already a wanted criminal of the court.

529
00:32:42,840 --> 00:32:43,560
Today,

530
00:32:45,160 --> 00:32:46,280
you will undoubtedly die.

531
00:32:48,920 --> 00:32:50,000
I never expected

532
00:32:51,720 --> 00:32:53,320
that you would choose to ignore your Godfather

533
00:32:53,320 --> 00:32:54,960
and Wang Zhi's actions,

534
00:32:55,040 --> 00:32:56,160
to escape reality.

535
00:33:00,120 --> 00:33:01,000
You've been through so much.

536
00:33:01,000 --> 00:33:02,000
Do you still not understand?

537
00:33:03,080 --> 00:33:04,680
Look at all this absurdity before you.

538
00:33:22,960 --> 00:33:25,840
I don't need you to lecture me on right and wrong.

539
00:33:58,280 --> 00:33:59,240
This smoke is poisonous.

540
00:34:00,600 --> 00:34:01,560
My surname is Tang,

541
00:34:02,800 --> 00:34:03,560
given name Xi,

542
00:34:06,160 --> 00:34:07,200
courtesy name Wanqing.

543
00:34:09,200 --> 00:34:10,760
Taken from "Heaven pities the humble grass,"

544
00:34:10,760 --> 00:34:12,040
"the world cherishes the clear evening."

545
00:34:13,760 --> 00:34:14,760
Though I am a woman,

546
00:34:16,760 --> 00:34:18,720
I was born strong and arrogant.

547
00:34:22,160 --> 00:34:23,640
It must be to bring happiness to others

548
00:34:23,640 --> 00:34:24,840
that I walk this earth.

549
00:34:27,680 --> 00:34:28,680
I should be proud,

550
00:34:28,680 --> 00:34:30,280
to live as dazzlingly as the blazing sun.

551
00:34:33,200 --> 00:34:34,480
Isn't this what

552
00:34:35,800 --> 00:34:36,920
you have always taught me?

553
00:34:41,160 --> 00:34:41,760
Tell me,

554
00:34:43,120 --> 00:34:45,520
where exactly is the Western Depot's secret mechanism?

555
00:34:46,360 --> 00:34:47,280
They are waiting for me.

556
00:34:49,680 --> 00:34:51,520
Are you really determined to do this?

557
00:34:52,960 --> 00:34:54,120
My will in this life

558
00:34:56,000 --> 00:34:56,960
will never change.

559
00:34:59,520 --> 00:35:01,080
A grown daughter really can't be kept at home.

560
00:35:02,360 --> 00:35:03,040
Fair enough.

561
00:35:04,520 --> 00:35:07,040
No one in this world can stop your will.

562
00:35:08,760 --> 00:35:09,440
Fine.

563
00:35:11,160 --> 00:35:13,400
Let me help you one last time.

564
00:35:15,040 --> 00:35:15,800
From now on,

565
00:35:15,880 --> 00:35:18,320
the name of Tang Xi, Young Mistress of the Tang Clan,

566
00:35:20,160 --> 00:35:22,120
shall live only in the Jianghu.

567
00:35:24,400 --> 00:35:25,160
The mechanism...

568
00:35:26,080 --> 00:35:27,280
is in the Imperial Tombs.

569
00:35:36,840 --> 00:35:37,920
You want to stop me too?

570
00:35:47,560 --> 00:35:49,040
Aren't you afraid of failing my parents?

571
00:35:49,600 --> 00:35:50,640
Children of the Jianghu,

572
00:35:51,120 --> 00:35:52,920
life and death are fated, riches are up to Heaven.

573
00:35:54,400 --> 00:35:55,440
When your parents eloped,

574
00:35:55,440 --> 00:35:56,640
they didn't bother to tell me either.

575
00:35:59,240 --> 00:36:00,560
If we all die together,

576
00:36:01,200 --> 00:36:02,400
we can burn paper money on the same day.

577
00:36:02,840 --> 00:36:03,520
How convenient.

578
00:36:13,920 --> 00:36:16,320
I've prepared two excellent steeds.

579
00:36:45,800 --> 00:36:47,080
Director-in-chief!

580
00:36:47,120 --> 00:36:48,680
Why are you discarding us?

581
00:36:48,720 --> 00:36:49,800
Director-in-chief!

582
00:36:49,840 --> 00:36:50,960
We are still useful!

583
00:36:51,080 --> 00:36:52,040
Director-in-chief!

584
00:36:53,520 --> 00:36:54,480
Don't kill me!

585
00:36:54,480 --> 00:36:55,640
Why are you discarding me?

586
00:36:56,240 --> 00:36:56,920
I am still useful!

587
00:36:58,680 --> 00:37:00,320
I can still serve you!

588
00:37:00,320 --> 00:37:01,480
Director-in-chief!

589
00:37:02,560 --> 00:37:03,760
Director-in-chief!

590
00:37:04,440 --> 00:37:07,520
Why discard me, Director-in-chief?

591
00:37:07,640 --> 00:37:08,440
I am still useful!

592
00:37:08,440 --> 00:37:09,120
Don't come any closer!

593
00:37:09,160 --> 00:37:10,200
Director-in-chief!

594
00:37:10,440 --> 00:37:11,880
I can still serve the Eastern Depot!

595
00:37:12,600 --> 00:37:13,640
Godfather is doing this

596
00:37:14,080 --> 00:37:15,440
all for my sake.

597
00:37:16,320 --> 00:37:17,600
It's all for my sake.

598
00:37:18,520 --> 00:37:19,400
Director-in-chief!

599
00:37:19,400 --> 00:37:20,880
He is doing it all for my sake.

600
00:37:21,040 --> 00:37:22,200
Director-in-chief!

601
00:37:22,960 --> 00:37:24,600
Why kill me?

602
00:37:59,400 --> 00:38:00,000
Zhang Yi!

603
00:38:00,200 --> 00:38:00,920
Quick, find Shen Youzhi!

604
00:38:00,920 --> 00:38:01,360
Are you alright?

605
00:38:01,360 --> 00:38:01,880
I'm fine.

606
00:38:02,760 --> 00:38:03,440
Go!

607
00:38:08,720 --> 00:38:10,880
Zhang Yi, you must survive.
